Hit, love. Not bit. But I'll simply go along with it.

* Zyber sat back, rubbing her jaw a bit.
There was the taste of mech-fluid in her mouth and she didn't know why, 
opening her optics to find herself looking at DeathScythes damaged knee she 
then knew why.
She grabbed a bit of snow by her side and reached out to put a bit of it on 
the knee to sooth the pain.*

" Oh, that was an accident. Sorry. This should sooth it."

* But before she could put the snow on the wound she was blown head over 
heals into a snowbank, not a sound coming from her.
She shock the snow from her, caughing a bit from the impact of the hit.
Zyber sat up, still covered with snow, half of her armor blown around the 
area.
She simply looked at DeathScythe.*

" I did not mean to bite you, it was an accident!"
